Name: arg_parse
Author: Stephan Aiche <stephan.aiche@fu-berlin.de>
Maintainer: Stephan Aiche <stephan.aiche@fu-berlin.de>
License: BSD 3-clause
Copyright: 2008-2012, FU Berlin
Status: under development
Description: Command Line Parsing functionality. 
 The module arg_parse provides an argument/command line parser for SeqAn apps
 including functionality to document tools and export the documentation/command
 line information to different formats like man, html, or CTD.